|url=http://content.karger.com/produktedb/produkte.asp?typ=fulltext&file=DEM20050195_6331
|accessdate=2008-06-12
}}</ref> Subtle problems with the [[executive functions]] of [[attention|attentiveness]], [[planning]], [[flexibility]], and [[abstraction|abstract thinking]] or with impairments in [[semantic memory]] (memory of meanings, and concept relationships) can also be symptomatic of the early stages of AD.<ref name="pmid15703322">
