}}</ref> [[Multilingualism|Bilingualism]] is also related to a later onset of Alzheimer's.<ref>{{cite journal | author=Bialystok E, Craik FIM, Freedman M |title=Bilingualism as a protection against the onset of symptoms of dementia|journal=Neuropsychologia |volume=42 |issue=2 |pages=459<U+2013>464 |year=2007|doi=10.1016/j.neuropsychologia.2006.10.009}}</ref>

Some studies have shown an increased risk of developing AD with occupational exposure to [[magnetic field]]s,<ref>{{cite journal
